:[{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"It forces a specific order of operations for the child and parent features. It runs the"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"child first, and then the parent. If the order was reversed, then it would be possible for"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"the parent feature to "},{"code":"nil","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" out the child state, in which case the child feature would not"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"be able to react to that action. That can cause subtle bugs."}],"type":"paragraph"}]},{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"It automatically cancels all child effects when it detects the child’s state is "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"nil"},{"text":"’d","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"out.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}]},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"Automatically ","type":"text"},{"code":"nil","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":"s out child state when an action is sent for alerts and confirmation","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"dialogs."}]}]}],"type":"unorderedList"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"See "},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/ComposableArchitecture\/documentation\/ComposableArchitecture\/Reducer\/ifLet(_:action:destination:fileID:filePath:line:column:)-4ub6q","type":"reference","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":" for a more advanced operator suited"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"to navigation."}]}]}],"variants":[{"paths":["\/documentation\/composablearchitecture\/combinereducers\/iflet(_:action:then:fileid:filepath:line:column:)-3kpqa"],"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"swift"}]}],"references":{"doc://ComposableArchitecture/documentation/ComposableArchitecture":{"type":"topic","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"The Composable Architecture (TCA, for short) is a library for building application